title: Celebrity Wife Swap S03E11 Jenna Von Oy Jill Zarin WEB-DL x264-R
description: "Blossom" actress Jenna von Oy lives in Nashville, TN with her husband Brad and daughter Gray. Expecting their second daughter, Brad and Jenna are hands-on parents who do everything together, including all of the household chores. Jill Zarin is an original cast member of Bravo's "The Real Housewives of New York City." Zarin lives in the lap of luxury with her husband Bobby, daughter Ally, and dog Ginger in The Hamptons. Zarin employs a staff that handles all of the cooking, cleaning and home maintenance needs. The Zarin family loves to entertain, and spend evenings out on the town.
